        IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
        PROGRAM-ID. LOANMOVE.
        ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
        INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
        FILE-CONTROL.
            SELECT LOANFL ASSIGN TO LOANIN
                ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED
                ACCESS MODE IS DYNAMIC
                RECORD KEY IS LOAN-ID
                FILE STATUS IS FS1.
            SELECT CUSTFL ASSIGN TO CUSTIN
                ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED
                ACCESS MODE IS RANDOM
                RECORD KEY IS CUST-ID1.
            SELECT TARGETFL ASSIGN TO TARGETFL
                ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED
                ACCESS MODE IS RANDOM
                RECORD KEY IS T-LOAN-ID
                FILE STATUS IS FS3.
            SELECT AGENTTFL ASSIGN TO AGENTTIN
                ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED
                ACCESS MODE IS RANDOM
                RECORD KEY IS AGT-LOAN-ID
                FILE STATUS IS FS4.
       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD LOANFL.
       01 WS-LOAN-REC.
            05 LOAN-ID         PIC X(6).
            05 CUST-ID         PIC 9(5).
            05 SANC-AMT        PIC 9(6).
            05 EMI-START       PIC X(10).
            05 EMI-END         PIC X(10).
            05 INTEREST        PIC 9(2).
            05 EMI-AMT         PIC 9(6).
            05 GRACE-DAYS      PIC 9(2).
            05 PENALTY-AMT     PIC 9(3).
            05 PAY-MODE       PIC X(2).
            05 TODAY-STATUS    PIC X.
            05 PROC-DATE       PIC X(10).
            05 TOTAL-PAID      PIC 9(6).
            05 NEXT-DUE        PIC 9(6).
            05 STATUS1         PIC X(6).
            05 TENURE          PIC 9(3).
            05 OVERDUE-AMT     PIC 9(6).
            05 NO-OF-EMI       PIC 9(3).
            05 FORECLOSURE     PIC 9(6).
            05 DUE-DAYS        PIC 9(3).
            05 DUE-AMT         PIC 9(6).
            05 RISK-SCORE      PIC XX.
       FD    CUSTFL.
       01    CUST-REC.
            05 CUST-ID1       PIC X(5).
            05 FILLER         PIC X(12) VALUE SPACES.
            05 NAME1          PIC X(10).
            05 GEST           PIC X(173).
       FD    TARGETFL.
        01   TARGET-REC.
            05 T-LOAN-ID      PIC X(6).
            05 T-CUST-ID      PIC X(5).
            05 T-NAME         PIC X(10).
            05 T-STATUS       PIC X(8).
            05 T-ACT-AMT      PIC 9(6).
            05 T-AMT-PAID     PIC 9(6).
            05 T-PAY-TYPE     PIC X.
            05 T-YORN         PIC X.
            05 T-BEST         PIC X(26).
       FD    AGENTTFL.
        01   AG-TARGET-REC.
            05 AGT-LOAN-ID      PIC X(6).
            05 AGT-CUST-ID      PIC X(5).
            05 AGT-NAME         PIC X(10).
            05 AGT-STATUS       PIC X(8).
            05 AGT-ACT-AMT      PIC 9(6).
            05 AGT-AMT-PAID     PIC 9(6).
            05 AGT-PAY-TYPE     PIC X.
            05 AGT-YORN         PIC X.
            05 AGT-BEST         PIC X(26).
         WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
         01 WS-EOF        PIC X VALUE 'N'.
         01 LOAN-ID1      PIC X(6).
         01 FS1           PIC XX.
         01 FS2           PIC XX.
         01 FS3           PIC XX.
         01 FS4           PIC XX.
         PROCEDURE DIVISION.
         MAIN-LOGIC.
             OPEN INPUT LOANFL CUSTFL
                 I-O    TARGETFL AGENTTFL
                 MOVE LOW-VALUES TO LOAN-ID
                 START LOANFL KEY >=  LOAN-ID
                 INVALID KEY
                        MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF
                 END-START
                 MOVE 'N' TO WS-EOF
                 PERFORM UNTIL WS-EOF = 'Y'
                 DISPLAY 'GGG' FS1
                 READ LOANFL NEXT RECORD
                     AT END
                         MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF
                      NOT AT END
                       DISPLAY 'HI'
                       PERFORM WRITE-PARA1
                       DISPLAY TARGET-REC  FS3
                       WRITE TARGET-REC
                 END-READ
                 DISPLAY 'AFT'
                 IF PAY-MODE = 'OF'
                    PERFORM WRITE-PARA2
                    WRITE AG-TARGET-REC
                 END-IF
             END-PERFORM
             CLOSE LOANFL CUSTFL AGENTTFL TARGETFL
             STOP RUN.
         WRITE-PARA1.
               MOVE LOAN-ID        TO T-LOAN-ID
               MOVE CUST-ID        TO T-CUST-ID
               MOVE STATUS1        TO T-STATUS
               MOVE NEXT-DUE       TO T-ACT-AMT
               MOVE ZEROES         TO T-AMT-PAID
               MOVE 'N'            TO T-PAY-TYPE
               MOVE 'N'            TO T-PAY-TYPE
               MOVE CUST-ID TO CUST-ID1
               READ CUSTFL
                    INVALID KEY
                            DISPLAY 'CUST-ID NOT FOUND' CUST-ID
               END-READ
               MOVE NAME1 TO T-NAME.
         WRITE-PARA2.
               MOVE LOAN-ID        TO AGT-LOAN-ID
               MOVE CUST-ID        TO AGT-CUST-ID
               MOVE STATUS1        TO AGT-STATUS
               MOVE NEXT-DUE       TO AGT-ACT-AMT
               MOVE ZEROES         TO AGT-AMT-PAID
               MOVE 'N'            TO AGT-PAY-TYPE
               MOVE 'N'            TO AGT-PAY-TYPE
               MOVE NAME1 TO AGT-NAME.
